<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm Groß zu Altenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Heinrich Rummel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Herausgabe der zu Mühlhausen beschlagnahmten 470 Schafe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l22">VVilhelm Groſʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l23">ʒu der Altenpürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l24">Lieber vvilhelm / vns hat fürgelegt
                                <expan>h<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Rumell vnſer
                            <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l25">Jm iiij<hi rend="sup">C</hi> . vnd <del rend="strikethrough">S </del> lxx Schaff tʒu Mülhauſen aufgehalten habt
                        / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l27">daʒ Jr demſelben vnſerm
                            <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> dieſelben ſein Schaff <del rend="strikethrough">vngehindert </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_140_line_1575448204885_555">on hındernüſſe </ab></add>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l28">vnd ledig laſʒen wöllet / durch
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l29"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Nicolaÿ
                                <expan>Epı<ex>ſcopi</ex></expan> Anno etc viij<hi rend="sup">o</hi>
                        . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm Groszen zu der Altenpürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Wilhelm, uns hat fürgelegt <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Rumell,
                        unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie ir im iiii<hi rend="sup">c</hi>
                        und lxx schaff czu Mülhausen aufgehalten habt.
                            <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir demselben unserm
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> dieselben sein schaff <add>on
                            hindernüsse</add>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> und ledig laszen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Nicolay
                            <expan>epi<ex>scopi</ex></expan> anno etc. viii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
